'''Cindev''' was the [[Starship/Legends|starship]]-manufacturer of the [[Series IV picket ship|Series IV Picket Ship]]. It shared its name with the [[Cindev shipyards]], a location in which the [[Scorpion-class Intercept Shuttle|''Scorpion''-class Intercept Shuttle]] was manufactured.<ref name="Codex">{{TORcite|exp=lots|type=codex|Scorpion-class Intercept Shuttle}}</ref>

